<DIV1 TYPE="dedication">
<PB REF="3">
<P>TO THE RIGHT WORSHIPFUL THE MAYOR, RECORDER, ALDERMEN, SHERIFF, AND COMMON COUNCIL OF THE TOWN AND COUNTY OF THE TOWN OF NEWCASTLE UPON TYNE, THE NATURAL PATRONS OF THIS WORK, THE FOLLOWING HISTORICAL COLLECTIONS ARE MOST RESPECTFULLY INSCRIBED, BY THEIR VERY OBLIGED, AND MOST DEVOTED, FAITHFUL, HUMBLE SERVANT,</P>
<CLOSER><SIGNED>THE AUTHOR.</SIGNED>
<DATELINE>LONDON, <DATE><HI>March</HI> 1&s;t, 1789.</DATE></DATELINE></CLOSER>
