<P>The upper clerk of this pari&s;h dying 1724, it was thought more beneficial to the pari&s;h to have an a&s;&s;i&s;tant to the curate, which was done accordingly the &s;ame year. His &s;alary ari&s;es from the fees of the clerk&s;hip.</P>
