<P>September 24th, 1739, Robert Swinburne, A. M. morning lecturer, on the death of H. Farrington; &s;alary 100l. <NOTE N="g" PLACE="foot">Of Univer&s;ity-College, Oxford.&mdash;He died April 17th, 1761.</NOTE></P>
