<P>JACOBUS Dei gratia Anglie Scotie Francie &amp; Hibernie Rex Fidei Defen&s;or &amp;c. omnibus ad quos pre&s;entes litere pervenerint &s;alutem. Cum in villa Novi Ca&s;tri &s;uper Tinam in vico de le We&s;tgate vulgariter vocato The We&s;t Spitle ibidem quod|dam
